WEBVTT

00:00.094 --> 00:01.562
Previously on "Bitten"...

00:01.898 --> 00:04.132
Accept Elena as your new Alpha.

00:05.201 --> 00:06.400
I do.

00:06.402 --> 00:08.135
Together we can fix this.

00:08.137 --> 00:09.169
How?

00:09.171 --> 00:12.170
It's not my father that needs to die.

00:12.195 --> 00:14.028
There is no need to test me, Jeremy,

00:14.030 --> 00:15.229
I will not betray you.

00:15.231 --> 00:17.108
This blood feud has cost us both dearly.

00:17.133 --> 00:19.323
If you can get
me close to Roman,

00:19.414 --> 00:20.747
I will see this through.

00:22.867 --> 00:24.066
He's coming for us,

00:24.068 --> 00:25.268
the red-eyed wolf.

00:25.270 --> 00:26.469
He tore my mother's throat out,

00:26.471 --> 00:28.003
like she was made from paper.

00:28.005 --> 00:29.939
Nick!

00:29.941 --> 00:31.274
Katia!

00:33.378 --> 00:36.779
My brother... and my father...

00:36.781 --> 00:38.914
Elena... save them.

00:40.785 --> 00:42.918
This premonition, if that's what it is,

00:42.920 --> 00:45.121
makes me fear myself.

00:45.123 --> 00:46.756
When will it stop?

00:51.229 --> 00:52.527
It won't stop.

00:52.529 --> 00:55.064
Not until it happens.

00:55.066 --> 00:56.298
It's not like a bad dream

00:56.300 --> 00:57.932
that you can just shake off.

00:59.403 --> 01:01.536
It will happen.

01:01.538 --> 01:04.205
A premonition is like
a dream in this way:

01:04.206 --> 01:05.774
it's not literal.

01:05.776 --> 01:08.109
It needs to be interpreted.

01:08.111 --> 01:11.513
I'm going to cause the
destruction of Stonehaven.

01:14.084 --> 01:15.549
I burn it all down.

01:18.121 --> 01:20.188
This house has a dark heart.

01:20.190 --> 01:22.623
There is brutality here.

01:22.625 --> 01:24.159
Despite everything that is good

01:24.161 --> 01:25.526
and worth fighting for,

01:25.528 --> 01:28.196
that heart still beats.

01:28.198 --> 01:30.498
You know what it is.

01:30.500 --> 01:32.232
The need to kill.

01:33.135 --> 01:34.568
Wolves kill to eat.

01:34.570 --> 01:36.537
Why do werewolves kill?

01:38.408 --> 01:40.941
To protect ourselves.

01:40.943 --> 01:43.243
Is that why Jeremy killed that woman?

01:44.980 --> 01:47.414
Humans can't know about our secret.

01:47.416 --> 01:49.950
It's our number one rule.

01:49.952 --> 01:51.451
Is it really your rule?

01:53.088 --> 01:54.288
I'm one of them.

01:54.290 --> 01:56.056
Not completely.

01:56.058 --> 01:59.293
This has always been a society of men.

01:59.295 --> 02:01.761
Roman, Jeremy, all of the Alphas.

02:01.763 --> 02:04.464
They're fighting for power.
This is what men do.

02:04.466 --> 02:06.299
You are not like them.

02:07.268 --> 02:09.035
You are one of a kind.

02:09.037 --> 02:11.671
The single most important.

02:11.673 --> 02:14.073
You're the lone woman in their world.

02:14.075 --> 02:16.710
You can see the cracks.

02:16.712 --> 02:21.147
You can feel the brutality of it.

02:21.149 --> 02:22.982
Maybe you're the flame.

02:22.984 --> 02:26.752
Maybe you need to burn.

02:26.754 --> 02:30.489
I want it all to change, but...

02:30.491 --> 02:33.359
I don't know how to
do that without death

02:33.361 --> 02:34.827
and destruction and violence

02:34.829 --> 02:37.696
and hurting the people that I love.

02:37.698 --> 02:40.466
Elena, it doesn't have to be that way.

02:42.269 --> 02:44.436
Change does not have to be cruel.

02:47.207 --> 02:49.641
Then whose blood am I covered in?

